-- Nordstrom November sales fall 12.1 percent
-- 
-- Thu Dec 4, 2008 9:17am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/04/us-nordstrom-idUSTRE4B344220081204

 

 (Reuters) - Nordstrom Inc reported on Thursday its November sales fell 12.1 percent to $707 million. 

 Highlights: * November same store sales fell 15.9 percent * November Thomson Reuters Estimates same-store sales view was down 17.9 percent * Timing of thanksgiving holiday negatively impacted due to one less week of holiday shopping (Bangalore Equities Newsroom)